title: American Diner Revival S02E02 Degreasing The Greeks PDTV.x264-JI
description:
American Diner Revival - Season 2, Episode 2




Degreasing the Greeks

The Greeks diner has been feeding the hardworking men and women of Kearny, N.J. for almost 50 years, but now this mom and pop diner is in danger of closing its doors because of its overindulgent greasy spoon fare. With less than two days to spare, can Chef Amanda Freitag and renovation expert Ty Pennington degrease the Greeks with a working class transformation and updated, hearty Greek items?




Original Air Date: 04-Dec-2015
